import React from 'react'
import {
    AppBar,
    Toolbar,
    ListItem,
    IconButton,
    ListItemText,
    Avatar,
    Divider,
    List,
    Box,
    Typography
}
from '@material-ui/core';

import {
    ArrowBack,
    Home,
    Apps,
    ContactMail,
    AssignmentInd

} from '@material-ui/icons';

export default function Navbar() {
    return (
        <Box component='nav'>
                 <AppBar position='static' style={{background:'#222'}}>
                       <Toolbar>

                             <IconButton>
                                                <ArrowBack style={{color:'tomato'}}/>
                             </IconButton>
                              
                                 <Typography variant='h5'>
                                             Portfolio                  
                                </Typography>        
                              
                       </Toolbar>
                 </AppBar>
        </Box>
    )
}
